<section class="home-statement">

  <div class="home-statement-content reveal">

    <p class="subtitle">
      A Way of Seeing
    </p>

  <h2>
  <span>Photography begins</span><br>
  <span>before the photograph</span>
  </h2>

    <div class="home-statement-text">

      <p>
        I photograph to share what the world, for a moment,
        has chosen to reveal.
      </p>

      <p>
        Before taking a photograph, I observe, wait and experience
        the place with my own eyes. I look for a change in the light,
        a hidden detail or a quiet gesture capable of transforming
        an ordinary moment into something worth remembering.
      </p>

      <p>
        Each image is an invitation to slow down, look again
        and discover how much can remain unseen at first glance.
      </p>

    </div>

    <a href="/about/" class="text-link">
      Discover the story
    </a>

  </div>

</section>


